dct_title_s: General map of China and adjacent regions, showing treaty ports and railways
dct_description_sm: prepared for the Department of State, by the Topographic Branch, U.S. Geological Survey.
Also shows railways in Japan, Korea, northeastern Vietnam, and Siberia, USSR.
"Compiled from China Inland Mission map of the Chinese Empire (1911), Stanford's Map of the Siberian Railway (1919), Imperial Geological Survey map of Japan (1911) ..."
